  <brief_title>Ramosetron Pre-treatment for PONV and QT Prolongation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Ramosetron Pre-treatment Time for Postoperative Nausea and Vomiting (PONV) and QTc Prolongation</official_title>
